attributes.action: We the people people call on Her Majesty the Queen to dissolve Parliament
attributes.additional_details: We have new parties forming as break away groups with absolutely no endorsement from those constituencies they do not have the mandate of the people
attributes.background: This government has shown utter contempt of the people of democracy of free speech and civil liberties of every single citizen off this country the corruption goes to the heart of government and the people demand that their parliament answer to the people
